  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carolina, a mailwoman with a lot of work to do (letters at the 21st century?!). Alice, a girl full of problems. Unravel the mysteries of those intriguing characters through this fun adventure where dreams and reality intertwine. The game has pixel-art graphics and a really complex story with many plot twists and good characters. The gameplay is similar to Paperboy and the old Mario games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141740/extras/cbfede6322cbf7a0dfe33ded11642ddf.poster.avif?t=1728778650\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141740/extras/cbfede6322cbf7a0dfe33ded11642ddf.webm?t=1728778650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141740/extras/cbfede6322cbf7a0dfe33ded11642ddf.mp4?t=1728778650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Comedy. Funny situations.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A Sidescroller camera like the old 2D games.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Platformer obstacles that the player needs to jump over.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A crazy story full of plt twists.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound Effects are from: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Musics were made using LMMS.</p>",
